         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00001-000-00191"/><rs ref="#pmb168" type="place"><unclear>b</unclear></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>fr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place"><unclear>wien</unclear></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>502<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>21<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>12/50</time>=</dateline></opener><p>ich freue mich sehr. es <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00615-1"/>gratuliren<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00615-1">Die Gratulation erfolgte anlässlich der <rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb35152">Uraufführung</rs> von <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29899">Freiwild</rs> am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1896-11-03" subtype="date-only"/> am <rs type="org" ref="#pmb35597">Deutschen Theater</rs> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb12740 #pmb24648 #pmb24645" type="person">schwarze koepfe</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb2337" type="person">leon</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb18308" subtype="implied">bruder</rs> doktor <rs ref="#pmb11253" cert="low" type="person">engl</rs> = <signed>richard +</signed></p></div>
